.------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.         Variables
.------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.
ADD       DIM       2
AMM       DIM       2
AYY       DIM       2
ACC       DIM       2
ACTION    DIM       1
ANS2      DIM       2
ANS3      DIM       3
.
CALLPOSN  FORM      1
CDESC     DIM       20
CONAME    DIM       35
COUNT     FORM      3
.
DANS      DIM       3
DANSOFF   INIT      "Off"
DANSON    INIT      "On "
.
FCODE     FORM      1
FIELD     FORM      2
FLAG      FORM      1
.
LNO       FORM      2
.
NEWDESC   DIM       20
.
OPERCODE  DIM       4
.
PAGENO    FORM      3
PRDIM2    DIM       2
PRDIM3    DIM       3
