.        Sub menus
.------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.
DISPSBCL  DISPLAY   *P50:18,*EL,*P50:19,*EL,*P50:20,*EL,*P50:21,*EL:
                    *P50:22,*EL,*P50:23,*EL,*P50:24,*EL;
          RETURN
